channel.title: Need help
channel.description:
Okay, I don't have much experience with P-Servers but after rage quitting from RS, I wanna make my own.
I've played on a few pservers for about a month so I know they work.
I honestly have NO idea how to code, or even get my own client up so if anyone could help me I'd be VERY appreciated.
If you wanna guide me through the whole then just PM me
Or if you have any links or stuff that would help post here
thank you,
bye

item.title: Need help
item.dc:creator: @Ceo123 Ceo123
item.description:
@Ceo123 wrote:

I made a few, you know like for fun, and they all went downhill from there if your a beginner then goodluck. TBH I thought it was hard with the portfowarding and all then it gets easyer from there. But If you dont have a VPS(Visual Private Share) Then your server will most likely not get popular. But I recommend using the Search Bar, and GOODLUCK BRUH
